#
# ‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT NOTICE:
# OpenWrt OS exclusively uses **Almquist Shell (ash)** and
# is **NOT** compatible with Bourne-Again Shell (bash).
#
# üì¢ POSIX Compliance Guidelines:
